data.description: Incredible opportunity to assume current mortgage at an attractive 4.75% rate. This residence showcases fresh paint throughout. Upon entering, you'll encounter a formal living space enhanced by charming shutters. Relax by the cozy fireplace in the living area. The primary living areas feature tile flooring, while the bedrooms offer the warmth of hardwood floors. Situated on a corner lot, the property includes an RV gate and a spacious backyard with a glistening pool, perfect for outdoor enjoyment. Its close proximity to Arrowhead Mall and the 101 freeway provides convenient access to shopping and entertainment. Plus, the solar panels ensure that your electric bills stay LOW!
